        "text": "=Topic for this video: {{ $('Get Next Ready Video').item.json.Topic }}\n\nContent Brief: {{ $('Get Next Ready Video').item.json.ContentBrief }}\n\nGenerate a Flux Kontext Pro image generation prompt for the Swiss realtor character 'Lorenzo' as described in your system instructions. Output ONLY the image generation prompt.",
